    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in great shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready for its next big adventure! It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so you can just hop in and go. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
