    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for car that is ready for the road today. Mechanically, it is in excellent health; the engine pulls strongly, the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, and the suspension remains firm and quiet. We have kept a rigorous maintenance schedule, and the most recent service included a full fluid flush and brake inspection. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a light scuff on the rear passenger side\u2014standard wear that does not detract from its overall sharp appearance. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with clean upholstery and a dash free of cracks or fading. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system, is fully operational. If you are looking for a solid, dependable vehicle that looks great in the driveway and performs even better on the highway, this is the one. Clean title and service records are available for your review.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle offers a refined driving experience characterized by consistent mechanical integrity and professional maintenance. Every aspect of this automobile reflects a commitment to quality, from its responsive performance to its well-preserved interior. This offering represents a superior balance of luxury and long-term value, ideally suited for the discerning owner who demands reliability without compromise.",
      "price": 34800.0,
