    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really wonderful shape, running smooth as silk! I've taken great care of it, so it's ready to hit the road for many more adventures with you. It's perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to chat more about it!",
      "price": 33500.0,
