      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example featuring the high-revving S54 straight-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a VANOS system refresh, ensuring the longitudinal and lateral dynamics remain sharp. The chassis retains its signature balance with a factory-spec suspension setup and hydraulic rack-and-pinion steering that provides unfiltered feedback. A true driver\u2019s car, it remains structurally rigid and performance-ready.",
